<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-02-16T11:30:48-05:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-02-16T11:30:48-05:00</published><updated> 2024-02-16T11:30:48-05:00</updated><title> Vision Pro 闪耀光芒</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Vergecast 团队的插图，顶部有 Vision Pro。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/jgcIdUeXfAG_UztoKcM3m73Eo-Q=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73144562/VST_0216_Site_post.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Alex Parkin / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;mw90OM&quot;>;对于第一天购买 Apple Vision Pro 的人来说，退货窗口已经到来，而且很多人人们表示他们&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/14/24072792/apple-vision-pro-early-adopters-returns&quot;>;退回价值 3,500 美元的耳机&lt;/a>; 。原因以及苹果可能需要采取哪些措施来解决这些问题，很大程度上说明了耳机的现状。还说了很多耳机的现状？马克·扎克伯格，显然现在是&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/13/24072413/mark-zuckerberg-apple-vision-pro-review-quest-3&quot;>;小工具评论员&lt;/a>;！&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;N0H7uY&quot;>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;uN4Ch8&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://pod.link/vergecast&quot;>;本集&lt; em>;The Vergecast&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;，我们讨论了对 Vision Pro 的反应、扎克伯格的评论以及 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/14/24070729/ray -ban-meta-smart-glasses-apple-vision-pro-ar-vr&quot;>;使面部计算机成为现实的不同策略&lt;/a>;。然后，我们讨论一些有关&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24073286/xbox-console-exclusivity-hardware-update-game-pass&quot;>;Xbox 的未来&lt;/a>;的突发新闻以及&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/15/24073457/google-gemini-1-5-ai-model-llm&quot;>;Google&lt;/a>; 推出了许多新的 AI和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/15/24074151/openai-sora-text-to-video-ai&quot;>;OpenAI&lt;/a>;。最后，我们在新闻中闪电般地报道了其他故事，然后完全出轨，抱怨......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24074795/vision-pro- returns-xbox-future-gemini-open-ai-vergecast&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24074795/vision-pro-returns-xbox-future-gemini-open-ai-vergecast" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24074795/vision-pro-returns-xbox-future-gemini-open-ai-vergecast</id><author><name>大卫·皮尔斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-02-16T11:29:25-05:00</published><updated> 2024-02-16T11:29:25-05:00</updated><title>苹果解禁了 Epic，以便它可以在欧盟开设 iOS 游戏商店</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Epic Games 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Dafd9P_T5mczn4xhklffUR6xZRg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/ image/73144556/acastro_STK108__01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;4puTEB&quot;>;Epic 距离在 开设 iOS 游戏商店又近了一步欧盟。作为&lt;a href=&quot;https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/news/epic-games-store-2023-year-in-review&quot;>;2023 年回顾的一部分&lt;/a>;，Epic Games 宣布苹果已恢复其开发者帐户，这意味着用户终于可以再次在 iPhone 上下载《堡垒之夜》了。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;24gGpS&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2024/1/25/24050800/epic-games-store-fortnite-apple-ios-launch-eu-dma&quot;>;Epic 首先宣布&lt;/a>;计划将其游戏商店和&lt;em>;Fortnite&lt;/em>; 一月份登陆 iOS，但尚不清楚苹果是否会授予其开发者帐户。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ovr7sz&quot;>;2020 年，在 Epic 开始使用自己的应用内支付选项后，苹果撤回了该公司的开发者帐户&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2020/8 /13/21366438/apple-fortnite-ios-app-store-violations-epic- payments&quot;>;在 iOS 版本的 &lt;em>;Fortnite&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 中，引发&lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2021/9/12/22667694/epic-v-apple-Trial-fortnite-judge-yvonne-gonzalez-rogers-final-ruling-injunction-breakdown&quot;>;一场漫长的法律斗争&lt;/a>;苹果的行为是否反竞争。但即使在审判结束后，两家公司都没有明显获胜，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/9/22/22687968/fortnite-ios-epic-apple-appeal-verdict-反垄断&quot;>;苹果仍然拒绝&lt;/a>;...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16/24074873/epic-apple-ios- Developer-account-eu-games-store-fortnite&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16/24074873/epic-apple-ios-developer-account-eu-games-store-fortnite" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16/24074873/epic-apple-ios-developer-account-eu-games-store-fortnite</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-02-16T11:18:15-05:00</published><updated> 2024-02-16T11:18:15-05:00</updated><title>索尼降噪 WF-1000XM5 总统日折扣近 80 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;索尼 WF-1000XM5 耳机的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/W-WbbcGBvH4seBwODvAiTEMfE1Y=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73144530/DSCF2249_Enhanced_NR.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;索尼 WF-1000XM5 比之前的型号提供更好的降噪和声音。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;edBbGe&quot;>;总统日是 2 月 19 日星期一，许多零售商已经以最好的方式展示了他们的爱国主义：通过大折扣说出电器和小工具的名称。抛开笑话不谈，实际上有很多优惠，我们在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24072881/best-presidents-day-sales-deals 的大型综述中强调了这些优惠-2024-apple-tvs-gaming-headphones-smartwatches&quot;>;总统日最佳优惠&lt;/a>;。尤其是 eBay 的促销活动，是最值得关注的促销活动之一。这是因为从现在到 2 月 19 日，&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ebay.com%2Fe%2Fdaily-deals% 2F24-rw7-presidents-day-main%2F消费电子%2F293&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F2%2F16%2F24073856%2Fsony-wf-wh- 1000xm5-8bitdo-retro-mechanical-keyboard-xbox-series-s-deal-sale&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;eBay 正在对部分产品额外提供 20% 的折扣&lt;/a>; - 包括已经购买的产品折扣商品，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ebay.com%2Fitm%2F155634031857%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge。 com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F2%2F16%2F24073856%2Fsony-wf-wh-1000xm5-8bitdo-retro-mechanical-keyboard-xbox-series-s-deal-sale&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;LG 出色的 C3 OLED&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;asc7Xq&quot; >;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Bose 的 Ultra Open 耳塞是迄今为止最大胆、最独特的耳塞&quot;,&quot;url&quot; :&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24073019/bose-ultra-open-earbuds-review&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您现在可以以 90 美元的价格购买一对 Sonos 出色的 Era 100 扬声器&quot; ,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/15/24073753/sonos-era-100-lg-c3-oled-tv-govee-matter-light-strip-aeropress-deal- sale&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;2023 年耳机世界一切如常，但明年应该会带来一些变化&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23999795/earbuds-耳机-2024-preview-apple-samsung-sonos&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;3we7PL&quot;>;但是，如果您不在市场上购买新耳机4K 电视，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23803374/sony-wf-1000xm5-earbuds-review&quot;>;&lt;strong>;索尼 WF-1000XM5&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a>;&lt;strong>; &lt; /strong>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23067645/sony-wh-1000xm5-noise-canceling-headphones-review&quot;>;&lt;strong>;WH-1000XM5&lt;/strong>;&lt;/a>; &lt;strong>; &lt;/strong>;还可以在 eBay 上以迄今为止最优惠的价格购买（通过 BuyDig）。 XM5 耳塞的性能非常出色...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16/24073856/sony-wf-wh-1000xm5-8bitdo-复古机械键盘-xbox-series-s-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16/24073856/sony-wf-wh-1000xm5-8bitdo-retro-mechanical-keyboard-xbox-series-s-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16/24073856/sony-wf-wh-1000xm5-8bitdo-retro-mechanical-keyboard-xbox-series-s-deal-sale</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-02-16T11:09:33-05:00</published><updated> 2024-02-16T11:09:33-05:00</updated><title>据报道，派拉蒙和康卡斯特正在考虑建立流媒体合作伙伴关系</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Paramount Plus 标志，这是一个被半圆星星包围的山峰的蓝色和白色插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/eclsmKyjcl_6CHgHVQw150Lo7Ro=/88x0:1033x630/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73144507/Paramount_Plus.0.png&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;派拉蒙&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ezN8ty&quot;>;两者&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/2/23944141/paramount-plus-gained-过去几个月订阅人数达 2-700 万&quot;>;Paramount Plus&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/1/25/24050251/peacock -subscribers-are-going-up&quot;>;Peacock&lt;/a>; 一直在努力吸引订阅者，以进一步巩固各自作为流媒体领域持久参与者的地位，但根据一份新报告，这些平台的母公司可以考虑建立独特的合作伙伴关系。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;fDomuX&quot;>;&lt;em>;&lt;/em>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.wsj.com/business/media/paramount-discussed- Streaming-deal-with-comcast-as-it-reviews-options-c5df6902&quot;>;《华尔街日报》&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;报道康卡斯特和派拉蒙最近一直在讨论潜在的流媒体合作伙伴关系看到 Paramount Plus 和 Peacock 作为一揽子交易一起提供给订阅者。除了使访问这两个平台比购买单独订阅相对便宜之外，此次合作还将帮助康卡斯特和派拉蒙“节省大量成本——从节目制作到营销支出。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;uF6wOX&quot;>;Word of ...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16/24074887/paramount-plus-peacock-partnership&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16/24074887/paramount-plus-peacock-partnership" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16/24074887/paramount-plus-peacock-partnership</id><author><name>查尔斯·普利亚姆-摩尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-02-16T11:03:17-05:00</published><updated> 2024-02-16T11:03:17-05:00</updated><title>十年后，斯派克·琼斯的《她》依然屹立不倒</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;机器人版“思想者”的 3D 插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/sWHanTk7zUIY-tm8uZTFd4qSi70=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73144493/246992_AI_at_Work_FILM_ECarter.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;埃里克·卡特的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;十年后，斯派克·琼斯的科幻爱情故事仍然比许多同时代的作品更好地描述了人工智能。&lt;/p>; &lt;p >; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24066233/her-ai-film-spike-jonze-joaquin-phoenix-scarlett-johansson&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24066233/her-ai-film-spike-jonze-joaquin-phoenix-scarlett-johansson" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24066233/her-ai-film-spike-jonze-joaquin-phoenix-scarlett-johansson</id><author><name>韩雪恩</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-02-16T10:11:27-05:00</published><updated> 2024-02-16T10:11:27-05:00</updated><title> Wyze 停电导致人们无法使用安全摄像头</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;壁架上的安全摄像头。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/IOZlJj9ViqZf3yMe9CNu453Nxv8=/0x0:1080x720/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73144326/Wyze_Cam_v3_Pro_4.0.jpeg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Wyze&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;gGybqR&quot;>;拥有安全摄像头、行车记录仪和其他智能家居设备的 Wyze 用户今天早上报告称，他们无法访问这些设备及其应用程序正在返回错误消息。 Wyze Discord 中的用户报告说，问题早在美国东部时间凌晨 4 点就开始出现，并且到美国东部时间上午 6 点，有关该问题的报告广泛出现&lt;a href=&quot;https://down detector.com/status/wyze/&quot;>;根据 Down Detector&lt; /a>;.&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;rV4fEc&quot;>;在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://forums.wyze.com/t/service-advisory-02-16-2024/289732&quot;>;Wyze 论坛帖子中&lt;/a>; 关于服务中断，用户表示他们无法通过应用程序连接到安全摄像头。相机似乎正在离线，用户无法通过应用程序控制他们的设备。其他人则表示，他们的应用程序正在崩溃，或者设备已从他们的帐户中消失。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;MYya2Q&quot;>;Wyze 没有立即回复评论请求或了解问题原因的详细信息，但 &lt;a href=&quot;https://forums.wyze.com/t/service -advisory-02-16-2024/289732&quot;>;更新&lt;/a>;...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16 /24074799/wyze-outage-security-camera-smart-home-down-offline&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16/24074799/wyze-outage-security-camera-smart-home-down-offline" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/16/24074799/wyze-outage-security-camera-smart-home-down-offline</id><author><name>佐藤米娅</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-02-16T09:30:06-05:00</published><updated> 2024-02-16T09:30:06-05:00</updated><title> Xbox的未来：有关微软战略转变的所有新闻</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Xbox 徽标的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3raF3u7MtqW7PmSX855v9P6-Iyo=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73142453/STK048_XBOX_A.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;从主机独占到传闻中的新硬件。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 24073286/xbox-console-exclusivity-hardware-update-game-pass&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24073286/xbox-console-exclusivity-hardware-update-game-pass" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24073286/xbox-console-exclusivity-hardware-update-game-pass</id><author><name>汤姆·沃伦</name><name>艾玛·罗斯</name><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name><name>阿什·帕里什</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-02-16T09:30:00-05:00</published><updated> 2024-02-16T09:30:00-05:00</updated><title>你听起来像个机器人</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;机器人橡皮图章文本文件的 3D 插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3tlzgTyYuGNZ_rF_bcA29vKaha4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73144155/246992_AI_at_Work_BORING_ECarter.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Erik Carter 的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;人工智能曾经很奇怪。现在“听起来像机器人”只是无聊的简写。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24067999/ai-bot-chatgpt-chatbot-dungeon&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24067999/ai-bot-chatgpt-chatbot-dungeon" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24067999/ai-bot-chatgpt-chatbot-dungeon</id><author><name>阿迪·罗伯逊</nam